Title: Fix precision in smart ping interval
Level: 1
Edition: cee
Component: cmc
Class: fix
State: unknown
Version: 1.2.5i1
Date: 1390560484
Targetversion: future

When using very small intervals for the host check while
using SMART PING then due to rounding problems a 1 second
interval could be reduced to 0. This has been fixed.
